OL,6,FA report published on Friday shows the
OL,7,Fsite was bought for around #6.3
OL,8,Fmillion by vendors Brockwell Group
OL,9,FBexhill Limited Liability Partnership
OL,10,Fin August 2022.
OL,12,FBut the Home Office completed the sale
OL,13,Fin September 2023 for around #15.4
OL,14,Fmillion, more than double what had
OL,15,Fbeen paid for the site 12 months
OL,16,Fearlier.
