OL,6,FThe sale came after then-prime
OL,7,Fminister Rishi Sunak vowed on December
OL,8,F13 2022 to stop housing asylum seekers
OL,9,Fin hotels and find accommodation in
OL,10,Fdisused holiday parks, former student
OL,11,Fhalls and surplus military sites
OL,12,Finstead, telling the Commons, "unless
OL,13,Fwe act now, and decisively, this will
OL,14,Fonly get worse".
OL,16,FThe statement in Parliament "generated
OL,17,Fsignificant pressure within the Home
OL,18,FOffice to identify and secure sites
OL,19,Ffor asylum accommodation at pace", the
OL,20,Freport said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/18
