OL,6,FThat same month the Home Office
OL,7,F"decided to acquire the Northeye site
OL,8,Fthrough purchasing it from the vendors
OL,9,Frather than lease the site" as
OL,10,Finitially planned, the NAO found.
OL,12,FBy January 16 2023 the Home Office had
OL,13,Finstructed property advisers to make
OL,14,Fan offer to the Northeye site vendors
OL,15,Fbased on completion within six weeks.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/18
