OL,4,Ctaxpayers' cash on migrant camp
OL,6,FThe site was one of four "acquired by
OL,7,Fthe Home Office under the direction of
OL,8,Fthe small ministerial group" and by
OL,9,FJanuary 19 2023 the group agreed to
OL,10,Fprioritise the Northeye site,
OL,11,Faccording to the report.
OL,13,FThe NAO said the group, set up in
OL,14,FNovember 2022, was made up of
OL,15,F"ministers and officials from across
OL,16,FWhitehall, including the minister for
OL,17,Fimmigration, and was chaired by the
OL,18,FChancellor of the Duchy of Lancaster".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/18
