OL,6,FThese positions were at the time held
OL,7,Fby Robert Jenrick, now the shadow
OL,8,Fjustice secretary after his failed bid
OL,9,Fto become Tory leader, and Oliver
OL,10,FDowden, who was later appointed deputy
OL,11,Fprime minister.
OL,13,FIn February 2023 planning checks
OL,14,Frevealed "high risk" contamination
OL,15,Facross the site and a further review
OL,16,Fconcluded the "primary contamination
OL,17,Frisk was from asbestos-containing
OL,18,Fmaterials in existing buildings and
OL,19,Fcontaminated ground".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/18
