OL,6,FA "due diligence report" also
OL,7,Findicated repairs to buildings could
OL,8,Fcost "in excess of #20 million" but
OL,9,Fthis was not mentioned in the Home
OL,10,FOffice's internal advice, the NAO said.
OL,12,FMr Jenrick announced on March 29 2023
OL,13,Fthat his government would develop the
OL,14,FNortheye site to house 1,200 migrants,
OL,15,Fwith the Home Office completing the
OL,16,Fsale for around #15.4 million on
OL,17,FSeptember 21 2023.
