OL,6,FThe group of ministers "dispensed with
OL,7,Fthe need for a full business case
OL,8,Fbefore approving the acquisition",
OL,9,Faccording to the NAO's findings.
OL,11,FThe watchdog's report concluded: "The
OL,12,FHome Office's attempt to acquire the
OL,13,FNortheye site within just a few
OL,14,Fmonths... led it to cut corners and
OL,15,Fmake a series of poor decisions.
OL,17,F"This resulted in it purchasing a site
OL,18,Fthat was unsuitable for that original
OL,19,Fpurpose and it paying more for it than
OL,20,Fit needed to."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/18
