OL,6,FIn July this year the Home Office said
OL,7,Fno decision had been made on the use
OL,8,Fof the site and it would "consider its
OL,9,Fstrategy and broader requirements
OL,10,Fbefore taking a view on the future use
OL,11,Fof it".
OL,13,FWhile the site "may yet fulfil a need
OL,14,Fthe Home Office has, it remains to be
OL,15,Fseen whether the acquisition of the
OL,16,FNortheye site results in benefits that
OL,17,Fjustify its cost", the NAO added.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/18
