OL,6,FKieran Mullan, Conservative MP for
OL,7,FBexhill and Battle said his
OL,8,Fconstituents raised concerns from the
OL,9,Fstart: "I know that's going to be
OL,10,Ffrustrating for my residents -
OL,11,Fespecially when the issues that have
OL,12,Fbeen identified were things they were
OL,13,Fwarning about that they really didn't
OL,14,Ffeel this site was the right place for
OL,15,Fit there were so many questions about
OL,16,Fthe remediation works how much work
OL,17,Fwould have to be done to make it fit
OL,18,Ffor use."
