OL,6,FSir Geoffrey Clifton-Brown, chairman
OL,7,Fof the Commons Public Accounts
OL,8,FCommittee, said: "Once again, rushed
OL,9,Fand misjudged decision-making has
OL,10,Fresulted in the Home Office overpaying
OL,11,Ffor an asylum accommodation site that
OL,12,Fis not fit for purpose.
OL,14,F"I am concerned that the Home Office
OL,15,Fdeviated from standard practice,
OL,16,Foverlooked warnings about the
OL,17,Fcondition of the site and lacked
OL,18,Fexpertise to properly oversee the
OL,19,Fpurchase of Northeye.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/18
