OL,6,F"The Public Accounts Committee has
OL,7,Fpreviously warned about the risks to
OL,8,Ftaxpayer money when departments forego
OL,9,Fdue diligence in making decisions at
OL,10,Fpace.
OL,12,F"My committee will be following up on
OL,13,Fthis issue to ensure that continuous
OL,14,Fmistakes are not made and public money
OL,15,Fis not wasted in future acquisitions."
