OL,6,FLou Calvey, director of charity Asylum
OL,7,FMatters, which campaigns for migrants
OL,8,Fto be housed in communities instead of
OL,9,Fcamps, said more than #15 million of
OL,10,Fpublic money was "thrown away on a
OL,11,Fcontaminated and dangerous site that
OL,12,Fshould never have been under
OL,13,Fconsideration".
OL,15,FShe accused the previous government of
OL,16,F"ignoring warnings so it could indulge
OL,17,Fin waste and carelessness, putting
OL,18,Fcruel ideology above everything else `
OL,19,Fincluding value for the taxpayer".
