OL,6,F"If more proof were needed of how ill-
OL,7,Fthought-out the policy of camps in our
OL,8,Fasylum system is, this is it", she
OL,9,Fsaid, adding: "Our new Government must
OL,10,Ftake the lesson from this fiasco, and
OL,11,Fimmediately abandon plans to place
OL,12,Fpeople seeking safety in any large
OL,13,Fscale site like this."
