OL,6,FThe NAO report said: "It is
OL,7,Fencouraging that the Home Office has
OL,8,Ftaken steps to understand what went
OL,9,Fwrong, and that it has made changes to
OL,10,Fimprove... But this case exemplifies
OL,11,Fthe need to adhere to minimum
OL,12,Fstandards and not forgo due diligence,
OL,13,Fespecially at times of intense
OL,14,Fpressure."
