OL,6,FThe Home Office noted the report was
OL,7,Fabout the actions of the previous
OL,8,Fgovernment and said: "Having inherited
OL,9,Fan asylum system under exceptional
OL,10,Fstrain, with tens of thousands of
OL,11,Fcases stuck in a backlog, we remain
OL,12,Fcommitted to ending the use of hotels
OL,13,Fand housing people in more suitable
OL,14,Fand cost-effective achieving better
OL,15,Fvalue for the taxpayer.
